{"tid":1391291,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個巴膠，見到咁多車長都支持抗爭，真係感動到想喊","createTime":"2019-07-31T11:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T16:26:22.000Z","uid":70704,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"898a32f5d6ccd8a13897f2fc34aeb93a50d2dbbd","tid":1391291,"uid":70704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/posts/2359551350798341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fposts%2F2359551350798341&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=c121d6ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/posts/2359551350798341</a><br />\n雖然show証支持呢個行為好左膠式玩膠，但呢次抗爭運動其間巴士車長都幫過唔少幫，包括不合作運動/封路等等<br />\n希望8.5大罷工，車長們都可以支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左mtr之外，其實巴士車長都係好重要既抗爭一群<br />\n車長請受小弟一拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為一個小巴膠，我都識好多車長，有無巴膠一起諗下我地可以點出一分力？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"051420614379779c04fc1bba59949fdb964840f8","tid":1391291,"uid":187755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:29:30.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"bcd328468b12eb4db6330afa44590f52874bcd99","tid":1391291,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"MTR班車長，比D骨氣，全香港人睇住你地，問吓你地自己良心，8月5日先罷工，仲有幾日你哋考慮，傾掂數都可以改。你地自己諗吓啦！"},{"pid":"7fe51e7dcfaa3a12d3cba7990c2460d167867b63","tid":1391291,"uid":70704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcd328468b12eb4db6330afa44590f52874bcd99","tid":1391291,"uid":119283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"